        {
            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大 滬股一周計跌逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後升幅擴大，兩市合計18532.61億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指全日報3913點，升24點或0.63%，今日開跌0.95%或37點，報3652點，已為全日低位，即反覆向上，下午突破上午高位，見3924，升35點或0.9%，全日成交7996.96億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指全日報13760，升153點或1.13%，今早開報13423，跌183點或1.34%，早段見13419，跌187點或1.37%，為上午低位，隨即向上，午後最高13842，升236點或1.73%，全日成交10535.65億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300全日收報4502，升25點或0.56% ; 創業板指數升23點或0.71%，報3295。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指一周跌44點或1.11%，深成指一周跌106點或0.76%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15800501-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 15:30:02",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓股連跌兩日 全週累挫近6% 首爾綜指收報5438點",
